== 模板介紹 ==

== 使用方法 ==
球員條目的空白模板（常用參數）：
<pre style=width:500px;>
{{Infobox football biography
| name                = 
| image               = <!--除個別情況外，不能使用非自由版權圖像-->
| image_size          = <!--px-->
| caption             = 
| fullname            = 
| nickname            = 
| birth_date          = 
| birth_place         = 
| nationality         =
| country             = 
| height              = 
| position            = 
| currentclub         = 
| clubnumber          = <!--球衣號碼-->
| youthyears1         = 
| youthclubs1         = 
| years1              = 
| clubs1              = 
| caps1               = 
| goals1              = 
| totalcaps           = <!--出賽總計-->
| totalgoals          = <!--入球總計-->
| nationalyears1      = 
| nationalteam1       = 
| nationalcaps1       = 
| nationalgoals1      = 
| manageryears1       = <!--执教球队，最多可填至49个-->
| managerclubs1       = 
| medaltemplates      = 
| club-update         = <!--足球會資料更新時間-->
| nationalteam-update = <!--國家隊資料更新時間-->
}}
</pre>

== 參數說明 ==
以下同一行列出的參數效果相同：
*name / playername
*birth_date / dateofbirth
*birth_place / countryofbirth
*death_date / dateofdeath

